quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,Ukuri kudakumirwa (umunsi w’izuka)
  69,2,Ukuri kudakumirwa ni iki
  69,3,Ni iki kizakubwira ukuri kudakumirwa
  69,4,Aba Thamudu n’aba Adi bahinyuye umunsi w’imperuka
  69,5,Aba Thamudu borekeshejwe urusaku ndengakamere
  69,6,"Naho aba Adi borekeshwa umuyaga uvuza ubuhuha, usenya"
  69,7,(Allah) yawubateje mu gihe cy’amajoro arindwi n’amanywa umunani bikurikiranye. Wabonaga abantu ari imirambo irambaraye imeze nk’ingiga z’ibiti by’imitende byaranduwe
  69,8,Ese urabona hari n’umwe wasigaye muri bo
  69,9,Farawo n’ababayeho mbere ye ndetse n’abo mu midugudu yabirinduwe (abantu ba Loti) bakoze ibyaha
  69,10,"Nuko bigomeka ku ntumwa ya Nyagasani wabo, maze (Allah) abahanisha ibihano bikaze"
  69,11,"Mu by’ukuri, ubwo amazi yarengaga inkombe (mu gihe cy’umwuzure wo ku bwa Nuhu, abamwemeye) twabatwaye mu bwato"
  69,12,Kugira ngo tubigire urwibutso kuri mwe ndetse n’amatwi yumva abizirikane
  69,13,Ubwo impanda izavuzwa inshuro imwe (ya mbere)
  69,14,"Isi n’imisozi bigaterurwa, bigahondwa inshuro imwe"
  69,15,"Kuri uwo munsi, imperuka izaba igeze"
  69,16,"N’ikirere kizasatagurika, maze uwo munsi kibe cyoroshye (ku buryo cyakwiyasagura)"
  69,17,N’abamalayika bazaba bakizengurutse (ikirere) impande zacyo. Kandi kuri uwo munsi abamalayika umunani biyongera kuri abo bazaba bahetse intebe y’icyubahiro (Ar’shi) ya Nyagasani wawe
  69,18,Uwo munsi muzagezwa (imbere ya Allah). Nta kintu na kimwe cyanyu kizayoberana
  69,19,"Bityo, uzahabwa igitabo cye mu kuboko kw’iburyo, azavuga (aratira abandi) agira ati \"Nimuze musome igitabo cyanjye"
  69,20,Rwose njye nari nzi neza ko nzahura n’ibarura ryanjye nk’iri (kubera ibikorwa byiza nakoze)
  69,21,Azaba mu buzima bw’umunezero
  69,22,Mu busitani buhebuje
  69,23,Imbuto zabwo zizaba ziri bugufi (yabo)
  69,24,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimurye munanywe kandi muryoherwe, ibyo ni ukubera ibyo mwakoze mu minsi yahise (mukiri ku isi)"
  69,25,"Naho uzahabwa igitabo cye mu kuboko kw’ibumoso, azavuga (yicuza n’agahinda kenshi) ati \"iyaba ntari mpawe iki gitabo cyanjye"
  69,26,Sinahure n’ibarura ryanjye
  69,27,Iyaba urupfu (rwanjye napfuye mva ku isi) rwari rwo rwa burundu
  69,28,Umutungo wanjye ntacyo wamariye
  69,29,N’ubutware bwanjye bwabaye imfabusa
  69,30,"(Abarinzi b’umuriro bazabwirwa bati) \"Mumufate mumubohe"
  69,31,Maze mumwinjize mu muriro
  69,32,Nyuma mumuboheshe umunyururu ufite uburebure bwa Dhira’a142 mirongo irindwi
  69,33,"Mu by’ukuri, ntiyemeraga Allah w’ikirenga"
  69,34,Nta n’ubwo yajyaga ashishikariza (abantu) kugaburira abakene
  69,35,None uyu munsi nta nshuti ari bugire (yamuvuganira cyangwa ngo imurinde ibihano)
  69,36,Nta n’ibyo kurya (ari buhabwe) uretse amashyira (y’abantu bo mu muriro)
  69,37,Nta bandi (bahabwa) ibyo biribwa uretse abanyabyaha
  69,38,Rwose ndahiriye ku byo mureba
  69,39,N’ibyo mutareba
  69,40,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) ni ijambo (rya Allah risomwa) n’Intumwa yubahitse (Muhamadi)"
  69,41,Ntabwo ari imvugo y’umusizi. Ariko mwemera gake
  69,42,Nta n’ubwo ari imvugo y’umupfumu. Ariko mwibuka gake
  69,43,(Ahubwo ni igitabo) cyahishuwe giturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  69,44,N’iyo (Muhamadi) aza kugira ibyo aduhimbira (tutavuze)
  69,45,Twari kumufatisha imbaraga n’ukuboko kw’iburyo
  69,46,"Maze tukamuca umutsi w’ijosi (uva ku mutima, utanga ubuzima)"
  69,47,Nta n’umwe muri mwe wari kugira icyo amumarira (ngo amutabare)
  69,48,Kandi mu by’ukuri (Qur’an) ni urwibutso ku batinya Allah
  69,49,Rwose tuzi neza ko muri mwe hari abahinyura (iyi Qur’an)
  69,50,"Kandi rwose (ku munsi w’imperuka, Qur’an) izaba amakuba ku bahakanyi"
  69,51,Kandi mu by’ukuri (Qur’an) ni ukuri kudashidikanywaho
  69,52,"Bityo, tagatifuza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"